{"tid":1186480,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(17/8) Steam《阿嬤模擬器》與史上最欠揍的「金孫」展開超溫腥的廝殺對決！","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T03:45:50.000Z","uid":37757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b67dfbe75b8c84c498237fe31cff0730c1fbafbd","tid":1186480,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/77/29/q5iWpqGbmKWcrqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F77%2F29%2Fq5iWpqGbmKWcrqc.jpg&h=97a23817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想看和樂融融溫馨氣氛阿嬤疼金孫，金孫愛阿嬤橋段的卡友可以點選上一頁逃跑了，你要的這裡絕對沒有www保證摧毀三觀的遊戲《阿嬤模擬器》（Granny Simulator）即將於8月正式上架，目前可以在Steam搶先體驗！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《阿嬤模擬器》<br />\n親情？不，這是一場戰爭！體力很差的阿嬤努力過著生活&mdash;&mdash;做家事、吃藥、為植物澆水等等，而身為聽不懂人話屁孩的金孫，唯一的目標就是用盡一切手段搞砸阿嬤的人生！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/77/29/q5iWpqGbmKWcrqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F77%2F29%2Fq5iWpqGbmKWcrqQ.jpg&h=504a6c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「雖然生活感覺像是被寶寶搞砸了，但只要看到他可愛的笑容，一切辛苦都是值得的。」我可不是在說這種搞砸www《阿嬤模擬器》中的金孫只有一個目的：殺死阿嬤！（註：阿嬤的目的則是要做完所有該做的事）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/77/29/q5iWpqGbmKWcrqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F77%2F29%2Fq5iWpqGbmKWcrqY.jpg&h=83af77a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以使用的凶器在家中都能取得，包括花瓶、鍋子，甚至是刀，這些都可以用來攻擊阿嬤，讓她在家中四處濺血。當然，阿嬤身為大人&hellip;&hellip;嗯，老人，優勢就是HP高血厚，雖然移動緩慢但大腳一踹也是可以把金孫給踢飛出去，或用毒噴霧讓屁孩痛到打滾，爽！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/77/29/q5iWpqGbmKWcrqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F77%2F29%2Fq5iWpqGbmKWcrqU.jpg&h=d40062ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金孫的優勢是行動敏捷不會死，還有專屬的屁孩通道方便行動，體積小動作快相當適合暗殺（無誤）阿嬤跟金孫兩方都是由玩家扮演，這當然不是一款家庭遊戲，但挺適合朋友們玩，要是玩到惱羞吵架了可別怪我（笑）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NgUfPPWILfY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNgUfPPWILfY&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=17605197\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NgUfPPWILfY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n38zN8EDhhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn38zN8EDhhg&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=e71cb56d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n38zN8EDhhg</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1647729?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=kakalopo&amp;fbclid=IwAR0wmAseC1_jbvgpgdqMkM2NmGDx84OXI3J6C9yspSj5FCSotd-U0ej6cqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1647729%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dkakalopo%26fbclid%3DIwAR0wmAseC1_jbvgpgdqMkM2NmGDx84OXI3J6C9yspSj5FCSotd-U0ej6cqQ&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=4f095004\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1647729?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=kakalopo&amp;fbclid=IwAR0wmAseC1_jbvgpgdqMkM2NmGDx84OXI3J6C9yspSj5FCSotd-U0ej6cqQ</a></span>"},{"pid":"ff2f61c0c3dea8c3170ccc65c90549d1a1a18b92","tid":1186480,"uid":159604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"個designer係有幾憎佢阿嫲"},{"pid":"4e8e1a721be32f910a385717236f7e707e821999","tid":1186480,"uid":11260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"好似好正，會唔會出switch"},{"pid":"517be1544be86d3c4ebbcdc829582ae70fa6effd","tid":1186480,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff2f61c0c3dea8c3170ccc65c90549d1a1a18b92","tid":1186480,"uid":159604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"個designer係有幾憎佢阿嫲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets